data.description:
Discover serenity and breathtaking views atop the Bigfoot Subdivision in the sunny Willow Creek. This immaculate 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence strikes the perfect harmony between cozy and spacious living. Start your day with tranquil morning coffee on the expansive new deck, offering unmatched privacy.
The property boasts a fenced garden space and a junior barn, ideal for storing tools and outdoor essentials. Inside, revel in the allure of new flooring and an environmentally conscious mini split heating and cooling system, ensuring year-round comfort. For added peace of mind, a Generac generator is seamlessly integrated, activating automatically during power outages.
Opportunity to assume a VA loan at an unbeatable 2.625% interest rate.
Schedule a showing today.
